<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-05-31T12:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-05-31T12:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-31T12:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Arm 和 Copilot Plus 上的 Windows 可能对 PC 游戏大有裨益</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;微软首席执行官表示新的 AI PC 将重振 PC-Mac 竞争&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/StCmC5gy53g3X78L3YLYWV_W2Jw=/0x0:4000x2667/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73380665/2153352890.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片：Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;P4a7hB&quot;>;Microsoft Build 的很大一部分上周我了解到 Windows on Arm 在 PC 游戏方面的潜力，尤其是笔记本电脑和手持设备。微软和高通还没有过多谈论这一点，但这两家公司都在暗示游戏兼容性。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;KhgB0f&quot;>;高通此前表示，大多数 Windows 游戏&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/24107331/qualcomm-gdc-2024-snapdragon-on-windows-games&quot;>;应该在 Snapdragon X Elite 笔记本电脑上“正常工作”&lt;/a>;，微软花时间在舞台上演示了更多游戏上周在构建中。 &lt;em>;《无主之地 3》&lt;/em>; 的运行速度比原生 1440p 分辨率快约 60%，这得益于 Microsoft 的自动超分辨率技术。这利用了 NPU 来提高帧速率和分辨率，就像 Nvidia 的 DLSS 利用自己的 GPU 来升级游戏一样。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;lEdWN6&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/5/21/24161936/windows-on-arm-ready-software-linaro-microsoft-qualcomm&quot;>;微软也...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/5/31/24168566/windows-arm-copilot-plus-gaming-pcs-handhelds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/31/24168566/windows-arm-copilot-plus-gaming-pcs-handhelds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/31/24168566/windows-arm-copilot-plus-gaming-pcs-handhelds</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-31T11:10:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-31T11:10:03-04:00</updated><title> “Quest 3S”可能是 Meta 更实惠的 VR 耳机的名称</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;充电底座上的 Quest 3&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ErFgmuVY4wJe4sbT0J_SoShExH0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73380518/236805_Quest_3_and_Ray_Ban_meta_glasses_BFarsace_0019.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Becca Farsace / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fXGpbf&quot;>;Meta 似乎已经确认了其下一款虚拟现实耳机：Quest 3S。在 Quest 商店列表中 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uploadvr.com/meta-quest-3s-name-confirmed/&quot;>;UploadVR 发现&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;&lt; /a>;，Meta 将 Quest 3S 列为受支持的设备。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aHAHwq&quot;>;在撰写本文时，您可以看到 Quest 3S 与 Quest 3、Quest、Pro 和 Quest 一起列出2 即将推出的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fexperiences%2F5379012005560059%3Franking_trace% 3D0_5379012005560059_QUESTSEARCH_8WS6qXhaX4xbBUimo_eyJwbGF0Zm9ybSI6ImFuZHJvaWQtNmRvZiIsInF1ZXJ5X3N0cmluZyI6ImFsbyBtb3ZlcyIsImxvY2FsZSI6ImVuX1VTIiwibnV tX2ZldGNoIjoxMDEsInNlYXJjaF9yb3V0ZSI6IndlYiIsInRhZ19pZHMiOltdfQ%253D%253D_eyJzZWN0aW9uX 2tleSI6IlNFQVJDSCJ9&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2 F2024%2F5%2F31%2F24168669%2Fmeta-quest-3s-vr-headset-leak&quot; rel=&quot;赞助nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;Alo Moves XR&lt;/em>; 应用&lt;/a>;。其他即将推出的游戏，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fexperiences%2F7067612163334384%2F&amp;amp;referrer =theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F5%2F31%2F24168669%2Fmeta-quest-3s-vr-headset-leak&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;&lt;em>;奇迹池&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta .com%2Fexperiences%2F7176684719116288%2F&amp;amp;referr